                                    <div class="textBox">
                                        The College of Medicine and Health Sciences - Yemen is keen to provide a wide
                                        range
                                        of means to support the educational process, the most important of which are
                                        laboratories equipped with the latest means and technologies, quality education
                                        and
                                        scientific material, in addition to providing a stimulating educational
                                        environment
                                        to acquire knowledge and efficient training to work in the medical fields,
                                        aiming to
                                        graduate a competent cadre to meet the requirements of society and the labor
                                        market.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        The College of Medicine and Health Sciences is also a model educational center,
                                        where equipment, laboratories and devices are available for each program. It
                                        also
                                        provides scientific material in its theoretical and scientific aspects through a
                                        set
                                        of means, the most important of which are lectures, seminars, scientific visits,
                                        scientific training, laboratories and specialization periods.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        To ensure the quality of scientific outputs, the college provides a set of the
                                        most
                                        advanced means in the field of medicine and health sciences, including modern,
                                        integrated laboratories equipped with computers, in addition to departments
                                        dedicated to anatomy, biochemistry, physiology, pharmacy, and medical
                                        laboratories.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        The programs of the College of Medicine and Health Sciences in Yemen provide
                                        prospects for teaching and scientific research in a wide range of
                                        specializations;
                                        as the college programs are designed according to a methodology that aims to
                                        enable
                                        the graduate to employ practical skills to conduct research and medical work
                                        independently. The student's performance and academic achievement are also
                                        supervised on an ongoing basis and through a mechanism that enables him to
                                        practice
                                        the medical profession according to high professional and ethical standards.
                                    </div>
